dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the Channel Islands in California. This layer is part of a collection of data created by the California Deparmtent of Fish & Game.These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers, and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
